title: Obari
author: Obari
content: Just as the topic implies, I have upto $6000 worth of sumcoin and I don't know if this figure is real or the project is a possible scam.Please I need help on how to swap this coin please or how to sell it out.Thanks for your time.

comments.author: light_warrior
comments.body: Here on the forum is a topic on this coin, you can ask there. Also, you can join and talk to people in the group in Telegram or write on Twitter. Well, in general, the coin is dead, as I understand it. In coinmarketcap "this project is featured as an Untracked Listing". I didn't find it anywhere else.

comments.author: noorman0
comments.body: It's just a dead project the developers are trying to revive. As for the price I think it was set manually in their wallet, no valid sources were taken even though their twitter said that $500 was touched even though no exchanges list this coin anymore.
